Starstomp came over to where Windlord was talking with the Maximals. She did 
think they were a bit too chevalresque for her, but they were good fighters 
and they had won her respect! She put her cloak over her shoulder (for those 
wondering, she is a female version of Gundam Sandrock) and said:
Thanks, you guys! Without your help, we couldn't have held that long! And 
with all the treachery there's been today, I think we all got out pretty 
good from battle... except Sarge...
